history.content:
The waitlist for the course is not full (although it's getting close).

The waitlists for many sections are full, including, I suspect, the waitlists for all of the open sections (although I didn't check all of them).

Hi, I was waitlisted for CS170 but I saw that other discussion sections were open and that the lecture was open, so I decided to try switching discussions. The only way to do that was to drop my waitlist and try enrolling in 170 again. I tried this and now it says that the 170 waitlist is full. Is there any way I can get back onto the waitlist?
history.subject: How do I get back onto the CS 170 waitlist?
